Articles.Content:
I have tried making a mod.

This thing definitely won't get any awards for quality, but atleast I tried and put real effort into it.

Here's the link.

https://spacedock.info/mod/2956/Starlight System Pack

It's a planetary pack that adds 12 (planning to add 2 more, so 14) worlds, 10 of which are moons and the other 2 are gas giants.
Fixed Sati and Jool's orbits colliding
